Desk Chat
=========

This project is a modified fork of the XiaoZhi ESP32 voice assistant firmware,
customized for the M5Stack Core S3.

Upstream project:
  https://github.com/78/xiaozhi-esp32

The upstream codebase is licensed under the MIT License. See LICENSE for the
full license text.

Desk Chat includes original modifications (focus timer, turtle UI, board
trimming, and related changes) distributed under the same MIT terms as the
upstream project.
